16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 12 O.S. 2021, Section 940, is
18 amended to read as follows:
19 Section 940. A. In any civil action to recover damages for the
20 negligent or willful injury to property and any other incidental
21 costs related to such action, the prevailing party shall be allowed
22 reasonable attorney’s attorney fees, court costs and interest to be
23 set by the court and to be taxed and collected as other costs of the
24 action.
